<concept id="syncing_ldap">
	<title>Synchronize LDAP/AD</title>
	<shortdesc/>
	<prolog>
		<metadata>
			<keywords>
				<indexterm> access tasks <indexterm>LDAP/AD
							<indexterm>synchronize</indexterm>
					</indexterm>
				</indexterm>
			</keywords>
		</metadata>
	</prolog>

	<conbody>

		<p>To start an LDAP/AD synchronization:</p>

		<ol>
			<li>Create an LDAP/AD Integration Configuration (LIC) file to
				specify all the details about the LDAP/AD synchronization. </li>
			<li>Upload the LIC file to Eucalyptus using
					<codeph>euca-modify-property</codeph>. </li>
		</ol>
	</conbody>
</concept>
